import defaultTheme from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/default'
import freshGreen from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/freshGreen'
import blueSky from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/blueSky'
import brainImpairedPink from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/brainImpairedPink'
import romanticPurple from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/romanticPurple'
import freshRed from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/freshRed'
import earthYellow from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/earthYellow'
import classic from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/classic'
import classic2 from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/classic2'
import classic3 from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/classic3'
import classic4 from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/classic4';
import dark from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/dark';
import classicGreen from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/classicGreen'
import classicBlue from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/classicBlue'
import minions from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/minions'
import pinkGrape from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/pinkGrape'
import mint from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/mint'
import gold from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/gold'
import vitalityOrange from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/vitalityOrange'
import greenLeaf from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/greenLeaf'
import dark2 from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/dark2'
import skyGreen from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/skyGreen'
import diyColor from 'simple-mind-map/src/themes/diyColor'

export default {
    default: defaultTheme,
    freshGreen,
    blueSky,
    brainImpairedPink,
    romanticPurple,
    freshRed,
    earthYellow,
    classic,
    classic2,
    classic3,
    classic4,
    dark,
    classicGreen,
    classicBlue,
    minions,
    pinkGrape,
    mint,
    gold,
    vitalityOrange,
    greenLeaf,
    dark2,
    skyGreen,
    diyColor
}
